# VAST SE Toolkit — environment configuration
#
# Cloud Backup (Google Drive / OneDrive)
# Set CLOUD_SYNC_DIR to your local sync folder path, then restart the app.
#
# Windows (WSL2) examples:
#   CLOUD_SYNC_DIR=/mnt/c/Users/yourname/Google Drive/My Drive/VAST Backups
#   CLOUD_SYNC_DIR=/mnt/c/Users/yourname/OneDrive/VAST Backups
#
# macOS examples:
#   CLOUD_SYNC_DIR=/Users/yourname/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-you@email.com/My Drive/VAST Backups
#   CLOUD_SYNC_DIR=/Users/yourname/Library/CloudStorage/OneDrive-Personal/VAST Backups
#
# CLOUD_SYNC_DIR=
